data.description: Gated 9.69 acres welcomes you to this ranch home constructed in 2006. The property's layout allows for clear sky nights with stunning views of the stars. The home itself offers 3br, 2ba and bonus room with approx. 2,000 sq ft of living space. Home boasts a 10x40 screened porch with a swing for those serene country evenings. As you enter the living room, you'll be greeted with luxury vinyl flooring, crown molding, and a cozy propane fireplace that heats the whole home on those chilly nights. The crown molding continues into the dining room and kitchen, which is well lit with natural light.  Kitchen features an island with bar, all appliances remain, including a propane gas range. The first-floor laundry room features a pantry with ample space. The split floor plan offers a secluded owner's oasis with French doors leading out to the front porch, a walk-in closet, ensuite with double vanity, soaking tub, and stand-up shower. The spacious guest rooms feature walk-in closets and some built-in shelves with a shared bathroom with tub & shower combo! The oversize bonus room has brand new carpet and is plumbed for a bathroom, which can easily be converted into 4th bedroom and 3rd bath! The comfortable couch in the bonus room conveys and offers more space for your guests!  Overlook backyard from your screened porch or deck with new deck boards where you will see deer and other wildlife daily.  Huge, lofted barn features four 10x10 stalls, tack room, feed room, wash rack, workshop, and storage room. Water heater in place will need to be connected to water lines.  Plumbing in place at barn but will need a septic tank.  200-Amp power, plus a 50-amp RV hookup! There are opportunities for renting out the barn for event space, such as Steeplechase or Masters. Conveniently located within 20 minutes of Aiken, Augusta, and 10 minutes to shopping, schools,  local restaurants and locally owned farms! If you are the outdoorsy type, the FATS mountain bike trails and Clarks Hill Lake are within 25 minutes of the front door. Overall, the property offers a peaceful and spacious quality environment for years to come
